INSERT INTO `cp_companies` (`id`,`title`,`title_breadcrumb`,`alias`,`content`,`sidebar_title`,`sidebar`,`id_cat`,`active`,`meta_title`,`meta_keywords`,`meta_description`,`strapline`,`displayurl`,`logourl`,`staggurl`,`clickthroughurl`,`source`,`id_source`) VALUES (1,'Tyre Shopper  Where Buying Tyres is a Pleasure','Tyre Shopper','tyre-shopper.php','<p>\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">Tyre Shopper</a> has been voted the UKs No. 1 online tyre retailer by independent review site Trust Pilot. In our opinion this is a truly well deserved\r\n    accolade for the website that has always focussed on offering maximum value to customers and ensuring that tyre buying is a pleasurable process.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    And considering that we are talking about plain boring tyres and not the latest gadget or gizmo or the current fashion trend, you will appreciate that\r\n    this is not easy.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h2>Is Buying Tyres Currently Stressful for You?</h2>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The answer to the above question is a resounding <em>yes</em> for an overwhelming 90% of people. Research has shown that some of biggest concern areas\r\n    while buying tyres is that people are unsure of:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>The right tyre size</strong>\r\n    </li>\r\n<br>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>Which is the best tyre brand to buy</strong>\r\n    </li>\r\n<br>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>Tyre performance</strong>\r\n        - Whether the tyre you buy is compatible with your specific requirements such as driving mostly on city roads or highways or ferrying heavy loads most\r\n        of the time etc.<br>\r\n    </li>\r\n<br>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>The budget</strong>\r\n        - Is buying the cheapest tyres safe? Are the exorbitant prices charged by some tyres worth it?\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n<p>\r\n    Have you faced these concerns while buying tyres? Or perhaps, you have faced other issues.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The fact remains that your tyres are the point of contact between your vehicle and the road. And tyres are important not only functionally but from a\r\n    safety point of view too.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>\r\n        <u>\r\n            And often when the true significance of tyres for your car dawns on you (as it probably did just now), the stress of buying new tyres further\r\n            increases, because now you know how important tyres are.\r\n        </u>\r\n    </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong><u> </u></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h3>But Dont Worry...Tyre Shopper is by your side.</h3>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a>\r\n    was established with the intention of not only bringing to you the convenience of online tyre shopping, but also to help you make informed tyre choices\r\n    that instil in you peace of mind that you have purchased the right tyres.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    We like to call this the <strong>Tyre Shopper Magic</strong>. And this is how the Tyre Shopper team creates this magic.\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <h3>Widest Tyre Range</h3>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    Tyre Shopper stocks the widest and most comprehensive range of tyres across brands and budget levels. All the leading tyre manufacturers offer products\r\n    priced at varying levels and the Tyre Shopper tyre range therefore includes economy, mid range and premium performance tyres. They also stock the widest\r\n    range of summer, winter and all season tyres. Tyres for specific purposes such as for commercial fleets or for off-roading use are also available.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h4><u>Thus <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a> is your one stop shop for all your tyre requirements. </u></h4>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Let us say, you wish to buy new tyres for your high performance sports car and also want to replace the tyres on the family mini-van. You can find the\r\n    right tyres for both vehicles, right here at <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a>. So the stress of looking at different\r\nplaces for different kinds of tyres simply does not exist anymore when you buy your tyres from    <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <h4>Ease of Finding What You are Looking For </h4>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    It is quite true that <strong>choice can be confusing and complicated</strong>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Tyre Shopper may offer the widest range of tyres, but that would not be of much help to you if you are unable to find what you are looking for quickly and\r\n    easily. Precisely to help you in this area, they have optimized their website design and navigation so that you can easily find the tyre you are looking\r\n    for.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h4><u>You have the option to search for tyres by</u></h4>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    (a) Tyre brand or manufacturer\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    (b) Vehicle make and model\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    (c) Tyre size\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    (d) Vehicle registration number\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    By far the most popular search options on the <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a> site are searching for car tyres by\r\n    vehicle registration number and by vehicle make and model.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h4>How the Search Works</h4>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Simply feed in the data into the relevant fields, and the system dips into the exhaustive database to display the best choices amongst the products\r\n    available that match your requirements.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    All search results are displayed along with the fully fitted price, and you can choose the option that you feel is the best fit for you.\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <h4>We Wont Be Beaten on Price</h4>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    When you visit the Tyre Shopper website, the first thing that catches your eye may be the Tyre-Shopper mascot pointing out to the above information. And\r\n    it is true.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The Tyre Shopper team is confident of offering the lowest prices amongst all online tyre retailers in every comparable tyre category. Their confidence\r\nstems from the fact that the team continuously keeps track of prices elsewhere online just to make sure that theirs are the lowest.    <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk/price-comparison.asp\">Detailed tyre price comparison chart</a> is available on the website for your reference.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Do you know about the unique Tyre Shopper Price Promise?</strong>\r\nWell this promise guarantees that Tyre Shopper will beat a competitors lower price (for a comparable tyre) by 1.    <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk/price-promise.asp\">Click here</a> for more details on this.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    All Tyre Shopper prices are mentioned upfront including fitting charges and any casing disposal and balancing charges. There are absolutely no hidden\r\n    costs, you can be sure of that.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h4><u>But we would like to make sure that you do not equate low price with low quality.</u></h4>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong><u> </u></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Tyre Shopper is able to offer the lowest prices to you because they strike the best deals with manufacturers/dealers on account of purchasing in bulk from\r\n    them and because of their established relationship with them and mostly because they are driven to offer maximum value to you.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Rest assured <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a> stocks only the highest quality new tyres from the worlds leading tyre\r\n    manufacturers.\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <h4>Expert Tyre Fitting Services</h4>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    Purchasing the right tyres, though important, is not complete by itself. The crucial aspect is fitting the tyre to the wheel.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Correct tyre fitment is important for wheel alignment and balance, which are essential to ensure safety during drive.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>\r\n        <u>Tyre Shoppers tyre fitting associate is National Tyres and Autocare which has more than 1000 proficiently skilled tyre fitting specialists.</u>\r\n    </strong>\r\n    <u> </u>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    National Tyres has more than 200 area offices all over the UK, so there is bound to be one close to where you live or work. Once you have finished your\r\n    online tyre purchase process, a National representative from the area closest to you will get in touch to schedule a suitable time for tyre fitting.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>\r\n        <u>\r\n            Tyre Shoppers mobile tyre fitting service offers you the convenience of at-home fitting, obviating the need for you to drive to a garage or\r\n            fitting centre in the midst of your busy day.\r\n        </u>\r\n    </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <h4>Offering Value to You Beyond Buying Tyres</h4>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    At Tyre Shopper, the concept is not about selling you tyres. Their aim is to help you choose the right tyres by making available all the information that\r\n    you need. And the company representatives are always there to <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk/contact_us.asp\">help and guide you</a>, should you\r\n    need assistance in any area.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Moving beyond offering merely tyre buying information, <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a> endeavours to educate you on\r\n    various tyre related and safety parameters for your own benefit. In our opinion, this is a good thing because the more you know about your tyres, the more\r\n    confident you become in choosing your tyres, which in turn reflects on your driving too.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Tyre Shopper considers it a responsibility to contribute towards educating motorists on safe driving practices. Being a TyreSafe member, they are further\r\n    motivated in this endeavour. You will find on their website articles related to tyre safety, news related to tyre industry, guide to tyre terminologies and\r\n    technical aspects about tyres.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong><u> </u></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong><u>We request you to go through them so that the value you get from your Tyre-shopper experience is maximised. </u></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h5>Awards and Accolades</h5>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Over the years, Tyre Shopper has received numerous Awards and accolades. These are important because they have come from customers just like you, who have\r\n    engaged with and interacted with Tyre Shopper and bought tyres from the website and most importantly kept coming back to Tyre Shopper because they were\r\n    satisfied.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Some of Tyre Shoppers recent honours include\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h6>Trust Pilot</h6>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/tyre-shopper/trust-pilot-badge.png\"\r\n        alt=\"trustpilot category badge\"\r\n        border=\"0\"\r\n        height=\"193\"\r\n        width=\"225\"\r\n    />\r\n    <strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    UKs leading third party review site <a href=\"http://www.trustpilot.co.uk\">www.trustpilot.co.uk</a> rated Tyre Shopper the top online retailer in UK. This\r\n    is especially significant since Trust Pilot ratings are based on actual customer reviews. An analysis of the customer reviews received by Tyre Shopper (on\r\n    Trust Pilot) is represented on the pie chart below.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img src=\"{siteaddr}images/tyre-shopper/trust-pilot-ratings.png\" alt=\"trust pilot chart\" border=\"0\" height=\"150\" width=\"255\"/>\r\n    <strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    You can see that maximum customers rated their Tyre Shopper experience as 5 star.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h6>Auto Express</h6>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img src=\"{siteaddr}images/tyre-shopper/auto-express-badge.jpg\" alt=\"autoexpress badge\" border=\"0\" height=\"114\" width=\"118\"/>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Based on Tyre Shoppers low price guarantee, wide range of products and availability of professional fitting experts, all of which maximise convenience of\r\n    customers and offer them maximum value, they were declared an Auto Express Best Site for 2011.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <h6>Experian Hitwise Top 10 Website</h6>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/tyre-shopper/hitwise-badge.png\"\r\n        alt=\"experian badge\"\r\n        border=\"0\"\r\n        height=\"128\"\r\n        width=\"103\"\r\n    />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Experian Hitwise ranked <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a> website #10 in the Automotive Shopping and Classified\r\n    category. The Experian rankings are compiled every six months and are based on monthly average number of visitors coming to the website during that period.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In the five years of our existence, <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a> has been present in the rankings 10 times.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    With so many positive aspects (as indicated by the Awards) and a keen sense of customer service excellence which they display, you will surely agree that\r\n    buying tyres from <a href=\"http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk\">www.tyre-shopper.co.uk</a> is indeed a pleasure.\r\n</p>\r\n',NULL,'Tyre Shopper is brought to you by Constant Price Monitor Ltd, which has been established since 1994 with the aim of providing quality tyres at the most competitive\r\n    prices on the internet. \r\n    <hr id=\"system-readmore\" />\r\n    Tyre Shopper is now the <strong><u>No.1 Online Tyre Retailer</u></strong> in the UK.     \r\n',635,1,'Tyre Shopper - UK\'s Fastest Growing Cheap Tyre Retailer.','Tyre Shopper, tyres, cheap tyers, tyres online','Discount Codes for Tyre Shopper - Promising to be The Cheapest Online Tyre Retailer with Price Promise Guarantee.',NULL,'http://www.tyre-shopper.co.uk',NULL,'images/tyre-shopper/emily.png',NULL,NULL,'0');
INSERT INTO `cp_companies` (`id`,`title`,`title_breadcrumb`,`alias`,`content`,`sidebar_title`,`sidebar`,`id_cat`,`active`,`meta_title`,`meta_keywords`,`meta_description`,`strapline`,`displayurl`,`logourl`,`staggurl`,`clickthroughurl`,`source`,`id_source`) VALUES (2,'A Comprehensive Review of Play.com','play.com','play.com.php','<p>\r\n    Play.com is one of the UKs leading online retailers offering a range of products with easy and convenient access to consumers.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/play.com/free-delivery-at-play.com.jpg\"\r\n        alt=\"free delivery service with play.com\"\r\n        border=\"0\"\r\n        height=\"128\"\r\n        width=\"393\"\r\n    />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Do you play on Play.com?</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Initially starting out as selling only CDs, <strong>play.com </strong>soon expanded its range to include DVDs, Blue-rays, video games, books, apparel and\r\n    even toys and baby care products.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    This makes <strong>play.com </strong>one of the most comprehensive e-tailers in the UK.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Play.com  History</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Play.com was launched in 1998 as Play247.com and formally became <strong>Play.com </strong>in 2000.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In its more than 14 years of existence, Play.com has evolved offering more products, schemes and rewards to customers. Play.coms focus has always been on\r\n    enhancing value to customers at every step and in every transaction.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In 2011, <strong>Play.com </strong>was acquired by Japans leading e-commerce operator Rakuten. Rakuten, looking to strengthen their online presence in the\r\n    UK, decided to do it through <strong>play.com. </strong>This by itself points to the position of strength <strong>play.com </strong>has in this high\r\n    potential UK ecommerce market.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    This is what Mr. Hiroshi Mikitani Chief Executive and Chairman, Rakeuten had to say about <strong>Play.com </strong>at the time of inking the deal.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    \"Play.com is not only a pioneer in the market, but also one of the UK\'s most successful e-commerce businesses.\"\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Play.com  What Makes an Overall Play.com Experience?</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>Comprehensive Product Range</strong>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    The purpose of online shopping is the ability to shop at ones own pace and convenience. In the physical world, departmental stores are favoured because\r\n    they are a one-stop shop for various categories of products and the customer does not need to visit several shops to tick off the items on his/her shopping\r\n    list. The same concept spills over to the online arena and ecommerce retailers, who have a wide range of offerings. They usually do well. Because after\r\n    all, when youre shopping online, you dont even need to move from aisle or one floor to another (as in a departmental store). Anything and everything can\r\n    be purchased from the cosy convenience of the couch.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Play.com </strong>\r\n    does not disappoint on this factor as it has an extremely diverse range of products. The various product categories on play.com include DVD, Blue-ray,\r\n    books, video games, clothing, electronics, mobiles, and toys &amp; baby products.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    A particularly interesting category we observed was titled Gifts and Gadgets and closer investigation revealed that this category is filled with gift\r\n    ideas for him and her, dads and lads, beauty, home decoration, favourite gadgets and so much more. We recommend that you check it out. It might\r\n    actually take away the stress of thinking up gifts for loved ones in the upcoming holiday season.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>In-Depth Categories</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    A very strong point of the <strong>Play.com </strong>ecommerce platform is the in-depth categorisations that are made in each product category. This will\r\n    help you quickly find what you are looking for. Or if you dont know what you want, the categories will give you a very good idea of what is actually\r\n    available so that you are better informed to make your decision.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In certain categories, we found very helpful sub-categories. For instance, in the video games section, there is a sub-category for Top Searches, the\r\n    books section has a sub-section called Book Charts that lists the top offers, best selling authors, recommendations and so on. Practically all the\r\n    categories have a best/top offers section. So if you are particularly value-conscious (on any day), you directly go into that section and not get tempted\r\n    by other, perhaps, more expensive options!\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>Loyalty Program</strong>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    Like any other online (or offline) retailer, <strong>Play.com </strong>offers a loyalty program to customers to keep them coming back. Here it is called\r\n    the SuperPoints scheme. You earn 1 superpoint on every 1that you spend on the website, and every superpoint has a value of 1p for subsequent purchases\r\n    on the website.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The gap between 1 and 1p is no doubt very wide, but as the superpoints remain valid for 6 months, it gives you time to accumulate points. Moreover, every\r\n    time, you make a new purchase, the superpoints earned for the current purchase get added to your existing ones and the entire set is updated to be valid\r\n    for six months from that purchase date. So the chances of losing out super points because they became invalid are quite less.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.play.com/Helpdesk/SuperPoints_FAQ/SuperPoints_FAQ.aspx\">The guidelines on superpoints</a>\r\n    are comprehensive and there is no room for confusion as to what happens to superpoints when an order is cancelled, or when you have pre-ordered something\r\n    and several other such scenarios.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    This is appreciated because often customers get miffed, not because they dont have the adequate loyalty points, but because they have no clue how the\r\n    points are being calculated or utilised. With <strong>Play.com,</strong> rest assured this will not happen.\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>Price Quality and Delivery</strong>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    These three are important considerations for any online store and <strong>Play.com </strong>performs positively on all 3 parameters.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Considering that the online retailer stocks some of the best and premium brands from around the world, the quality issue is automatically taken care of.\r\nAnd in any case, there is a    <a href=\"http://www.play.com/Helpdesk/General_questions_about_Play_com/Terms_and_Conditions.aspx#right_to_cancel___unwanted_items\">return/refund policy</a>\r\n    in case you have a problem or are not 100% satisfied with your purchase.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Play.com </strong>\r\nstrives to offer the best price on all products at all times. You can redeem discount vouchers and coupons offered by third parties for purchase on    <strong>Play.com</strong>.<strong> </strong>The website offers a wide range of products advertised as under 5 and you can subscribe to the deal of the\r\n    day where you get daily alerts for the most value deal for that day.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    By default, delivery is free for all UK orders as well orders shipped to Europe (<strong>Play.com </strong>supports payment in Sterling as well as Euro).\r\n    But in certain cases, when getting the product is more important than paying a little extra, you can opt for express delivery options that have an\r\nassociated additional cost component. You can refer to the details    <a href=\"http://www.play.com/Helpdesk/Getting_started/Play_com_delivery_policy.html\">at this page</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Value Added Services from Play.com</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    As part of delivering additional value to customers, <strong>Play.com </strong>has incorporated two services (well one is a product and other a\r\n    service).These are:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>Play.com Credit Card (Product)</strong>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    Launched recently, the Play.com credit card can be used for purchase on <strong>Play.com </strong>as well as other places, just like a regular credit card.\r\n    On <strong>Play.com </strong>purchases, you earn 2PlayPoints for every 1 spent, while in other places it is 1 PlayPoint per 1spend. 1000 PlayPoints earn\r\n    a 10 <strong>Play.com </strong>gift voucher.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    There is no annual fee for the credit card, set up is easy and paperless. And you get 1500 bonus PlayPoints if you spend 150 within 3 months getting your\r\n    credit card.\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        <strong>PlayTrade Service</strong>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    PlayTrade is a portal within the <strong>Play.com </strong>website that allows you to put up products for sale and contact buyers directly. And this is not\r\n    restricted to individuals. Even established retailers can be part of PlayTrade and directly sell to you, a <strong>Play.com </strong>customer.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Though it would appear that this service is directly competing with what <strong>Play.com </strong>does, closer inspection reveals that this is a unique\r\n    service that adds more value to <strong>Play.com </strong>members.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The items that appear for sale on PlayTrade are usually unique items from individual collections that you may not find elsewhere. Or they may be used\r\n    items (in good condition) like CDs and games, which are now obviously available at a price advantage.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    You can sign up as a PlayTrader or access PlayTrade through your regular <strong>Play.com </strong>account. The company makes no imposition on prices, and\r\n    PlayTraders are free to fix the price they deem fit for their products. PlayTrade orders are processed through <strong>Play.com </strong>secure servers and\r\ncovered by the companys    <a href=\"http://www.play.com/Helpdesk/Getting_started_with_PT/PlayTrade_User_Agreement.aspx#5__the_fairplay_guarantee\">FairPlay guarantee</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Play.com- Winning Accolades Over the Years</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    While Amazon continues to remain the top online retailer in the UK, (as in many other parts of the world), play.com is usually within the top 10 spots in\r\n    rankings compiled by various third party agencies periodically.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In the latest IMRG Experian Hitwise Hot Shops List (as of May 2012). Play.com was ranked at #8.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/play.com/experian-hitwise-winner.jpg\"\r\n        alt=\"free delivery service with play.com\"\r\n        border=\"0\"\r\n        height=\"71\"\r\n        width=\"227\"\r\n    />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Play.com was #8 on this list for May 2012.</strong>\r\n    <strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    You can view the entire list <a href=\"http://www.hitwise.com/uk/press-centre/press-releases/imrg-experian-hitwise-hot-shops-list-may-2012/\">here</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In 2009, Play.com that specialises in music CDs and videos was placed the second favourite online retailer in this category in the UK behind Amazon.\r\n    However, in the same year, the National Consumer Satisfaction Index survey placed <strong>Play.com </strong>at the numero uno position ahead of\r\nAmazon.co.uk and i-Tunes, indicating greater degree of customer satisfaction associated with the company. You can read the details    <a href=\"http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/content_display/industry/news/e3ieda4f2f47125746da816749f5c0f4caa\">here.</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Security Breach?</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    A snippet of data we would like to share here. In 2011, <strong>Play.com </strong>admitted that owing to irregular activities by third party associates\r\n    of the company, a possible security breach of customer email addresses had occurred and customers were receiving spam on their email ids used exclusively\r\n    for <strong>Play.com. </strong>Though the company apologised and reassured customers that sensitive data (credit card numbers) was secure, it did leave\r\n    many uneasy.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Of course since then no other such incident has occurred.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Conclusion</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In our opinion, <strong>Play.com </strong>is one of the best sites for your online shopping excursions. In the course of our research, we found that\r\n    overall customer reviews about the company are positive, though there were some negative reviews too. But taking all facts into consideration, we would\r\n    give a big thumbs-up to <strong>Play.com</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    So if you are getting discount vouchers or codes for <strong>Play.com, </strong>our advice would be to grab them and use them before someone else does.\r\n</p>',NULL,'\t<img src=\"{siteaddr}images/tyre-shopper/emily.png\" class=\"theStagg\" />\r\n\t<div id=\"sidebar-merchantDescription-main\"><h3>Quick Glance</h3>\r\n\t<div class=\"readmore-on\">Description\r\n    <span class=\"readmore-link\">... <a href=\"#\" class=\"readmore-merchantintro\">Read More &raquo;</a></span>\r\n    <div style=\"display: none;\" class=\"readmore-off\">\r\n    Readmore description.     \r\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"readless-merchantintro\">Read Less &laquo;</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <ul><li class=\"official-website\"><h4>Official Website</h4><a href=\"http://www.play.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.play.com</a></li></ul>\r\n    </div>',6,1,'Play.com - A Comprehensive Review.','CDs, DVDs, Games, Entertainment','Discount Codes for Play.com - Great prices on Entertainment DVDs, Games, Electronics and more.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0');
INSERT INTO `cp_companies` (`id`,`title`,`title_breadcrumb`,`alias`,`content`,`sidebar_title`,`sidebar`,`id_cat`,`active`,`meta_title`,`meta_keywords`,`meta_description`,`strapline`,`displayurl`,`logourl`,`staggurl`,`clickthroughurl`,`source`,`id_source`) VALUES (3,'A Comprehensive Review of Screwfix.com','Screwfix','screwfix.php','\r\n<p>\r\n    Screwfix Direct is UKs leading online and direct supplier of tools, hardware products and accessories for trade as well as serious DIY enthusiasts. The\r\n    company has been serving its customers and this industry for close to 3 decades, having been established in 1979.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/screwfix/screwfix.jpg\"\r\n        alt=\"Screwfix logo\"\r\n        height=\"91\"\r\n        width=\"352\"\r\n    />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Tracking the Growth of Screwfix</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Rarely one comes across a company that has been on such a positive growth trajectory as <a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/container.jsp\">Screwfix.</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Starting as a company that sold only screws to customers via a direct mail order catalogue (the catalogue comprised a single page), Screwfix was then\r\n    called the Woodscrew Supply Company. By 1987, the product offerings had expanded to include different kinds of trade tools and hardware products. The\r\n    catalogue correspondingly grew to 4 pages and was now called Handimail.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The first Screwfix Direct catalogue was produced in 1992. By this time the company turnover had increased to 4 million. Growth continued and Screwfix\r\n    was taken over by Europes largest home improvement retailer <a href=\"http://www.kingfisher.com/index.asp\">Kingfisher Group</a>. This business partnership\r\n    made available more financial resources to Screwfix, further fuelling its growth.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Its blazing growth trail only reiterates the companys commitment to excellence in customer service.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Want to Meet Screwfix in Person?</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Several large online retailers have no physical presence. And many a time, you might feel more comfortable actually talking to someone, perhaps, taking\r\n    their opinion, when you wish to buy a tool. In such cases, then you would have to go to your local hardware stores that may or may not have the product.\r\n    Also they will definitely not be able to offer you the price advantage of big retailers like Screwfix.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    However Screwfix Direct has physical stores called trade counters all over UK, so that you can actually meet Screwfix in person. The first trade\r\n    counter was opened in 2004. As of September 2012, there are 250 Screwfix stores in the country and increasing rapidly.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The Screwfix direct website enables you to easily locate a branch closest to you.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Screwfix.com- Making it Easier for You to Buy</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Screwfix offers the widest range of tools and gadgets and hardware accessories. Practically anything and everything you need, whether for a DIY home\r\n    project or as a tradesman for your own business or as a company catering to customers, you will find it at Screwfix.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    And what is more, Screwfix.com makes it very easy to find what you want so that you dont get the feeling of looking for a needle in the haystack.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The website home page has various categories such as tools, heating and plumbing, Safety and Workwear, Automotive, Outdoor and Gardening etc, so\r\n    you can choose the specific category you are interested in and review the available tools. Of course, if you are a pro, you already know what you want and\r\n    the categories only make it easier to locate them.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Screwfix promises the best (and lowest) prices on all their products. In addition, they have a Deal of the Day, where a particular item is available at\r\n    the lowest price on just that day. And dont forget to check the Clearance section where you are assured of the best possible prices always.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong><u>Value Added Services to Customers</u></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Screwfix offers following services to you.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    1. <strong>Free Catalogue</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The Screwfix catalogue is available for free.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/screwfix/catalogue.jpg\"\r\n        alt=\"screwfix catalogue\"\r\n        border=\"0\"\r\n        height=\"208\"\r\n        width=\"146\"\r\n    />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Screwfix catalogue</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    You only have to sign in by providing the account details and request for the catalogue, which will be delivered by mail. Currently, issue no 111 is out\r\n    and you can choose from the vast of products and the best deals available there.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    2. <strong>24-hour Delivery</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Screwfix assures delivery within 24 hours for all orders in most geographical areas. There is no delivery charge on orders above 50 for regular delivery\r\n    options. Premium and special weekend delivery options are available. Screwfix does service Northern Ireland, the Highlands and other zones, where delivery\r\n    may take longer. <a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/help/delivery.jsp\">Click here</a> for more details on delivery.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    However, if you dont want to wait for delivery, you can use the <a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/help/click.jsp\">click and collect</a> option. On\r\n    selected items, you can make the payment online (so no waiting at the crowded store) and collect the item from your nearest branch (no waiting for\r\n    delivery).\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    This innovative service is proof that Team Screwfix Direct is constantly thinking of ways to make things easier for their customers YOU.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    3. <strong>Incentives for Recommending a Friend</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    With the great service, extensive product range and overall positive experience at Screwfix, you would probably recommend it to a friend, anyway. But did\r\n    you know that the company has a unique way of thanking you for the recommendation by sending you a 10 discount voucher.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nYou can pick up your Recommend a Mate card from any of the Screw fix stores or download it from the website.    <a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/help/recommendamate.jsp\">Here are the details</a> of how it works.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    4. <strong>Comprehensive Safety Guide</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Working with power tools and hardware products poses certain safety hazards and it is important that you are aware of these. The Screwfix catalogue\r\n    mentions the relevant safety code by the side of the equipment. But do those codes (often represented by alpha-numericals) make any sense to you? Most\r\n    likely <strong><em>no</em></strong>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    To help you out, Screw fix has compiled an easy to use, handy <a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/help/healthandsafety.jsp\">health and safety guide</a>\r\n    that explains what those codes and phrases stand for and helps you use your tools more safely.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Are You a Business Customer? </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Are you in the hardware/tradesman business yourself? Or does your company service other users of these products? Screwfix realises that business purchases\r\n    are different from personal purchases and demand certain specific services. Hence they have a separate Business Services section just for you.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Besides an unparalleled product range that stocks the worlds top quality brands, you can look forward to the best trade prices in the country. Quotations\r\n    are offered for tenders and further exclusive offers and customised discounts are available for bulk orders. Deliveries are made on time, as promised.\r\n    Screwfix has an impressive service level of 99.5% for delivery on time.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    For an even more seamless integration of the procurement process in your system, you can upload the Screwfix catalogue directly in your supply chain\r\n    software and save administration time and costs.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Screwfix Trade Credit Account- Manage Your Purchases and Cashflow</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    One of the biggest value additions to business customers is the Screwfix Trade Credit Account. Offered by Screwfix in conjunction with Trade UK, it is a\r\n    simple system wherein you get a Trade Account at Screwfix as well as a card. With this account you are eligible for up to 60 days free credit that can do\r\n    wonders for your cashflow. There are no annual charges for this card. You also get extra cards for employees. You can view all card activity online through\r\n    your account. And you can make consolidated payments when you receive your monthly statements. You can view your monthly statements online too.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>But that is not All</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Screwfix Direct, admittedly offering the best and highest quality of tools and products, still realises that there may be situations where you do not like\r\n    what you do get. And there is also the chance that you may have received a faulty piece. (There is the odd faulty piece even in the best manufacturers\r\n    batch). Hence the company offers you a 30 day money back guarantee and you can return the product. Of course there are certain conditions attached. You can\r\n    see the <a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/help/returns.jsp\">details here</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Britains Top Tradesman Award</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Screwfix conducts an annual competition to identify Britains top tradesman. The Award is considered a prestigious honour in the industry and trade\r\n    community. Being the top retailer in this category, this award is an extension of the Screwfix brand.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/screwfix/top-tradesman.jpg\"\r\n        alt=\"top tradesman badge\"\r\n        border=\"0\"\r\n        height=\"209\"\r\n        width=\"278\"\r\n    />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The competition brings to fore talented and hardworking tradesmen from around the nation. There are several regional rounds, culminating in one grand\r\n    nationwide finale. The exposure and recognition received by the regional and national finalists does wonders for their business. And naturally the winner\r\nexperiences the maximum benefits. Here is what 2011    <a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/landing.jsp?id=BritainsTopTradesmans\">Screwfix Top Britains Tradesman</a> Paul Martin says about how the honour\r\n    changed his business and life.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In 2012, Renault partnered with Screwfix for this Award to find <em>Britains Top Tradesman</em>. And the grand prize is a van from Renaults award winning\r\n    range with a value of upto 27,000.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <img\r\n        src=\"{siteaddr}images/screwfix/screwfix-Renault.jpg\"\r\n        alt=\"screwfix and Renault relationship\"\r\n        border=\"0\"\r\n        height=\"114\"\r\n        width=\"441\"\r\n    />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>The 2012 Top Tradesman Award</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Michael Cairns of <a href=\"http://www.celsiusplumbingandheating.com/blog/20-michael-wins-britains-top-tradesman\">Celsius Plumbing and Heating</a> is\r\n    Britains Top Tradesman 2012.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>Conclusion</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Our overall review for Screwfix is extremely positive. It is one of the best choices for your tools and hardware requirements. The company is committed to\r\n    excellent service standards and goes out of its way to make your overall experience stress free and convenient.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    In the end, we would like to leave you with some numbers to give you some perspective.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    1. The online Screwfix.com store stocks over 17,000 products available for ready delivery within 24 hours.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    2. The company has 250 physical stores that stock close to 10,000 products that can be picked up instantly. The plan is to add 100 more stores by the end\r\n    of 2012.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    3. There are over 3500 employees including 400 people in the Contact Centre.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    4. The Contact Centre handles 40,000 calls, and thousands of email and postal enquiries every week.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    5. Screwfix sells 269 miles of cable, 6300 saws and whooping 18million screws, all in a week.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    So any discount codes or coupons for Screwfix, grab them without a second thought.\r\n</p>',NULL,'<img src=\"{siteaddr}images/tyre-shopper/emily.png\" class=\"theStagg\" />\r\n\t<div id=\"sidebar-merchantDescription-main\">\r\n\t<div class=\"readmore-on\">Screwfix Direct is UKs leading online and direct supplier of tools, hardware products and accessories for trade as well as serious DIY enthusiasts.\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    </div>\r\n    <ul><li class=\"official-website\"><h4>Official Website</h4><a href=\"http://www.screwfix.com/jsp/container.jsp\" target=\"_blank\">www.screwfix.com</a></li></ul>\r\n    </div>',4,1,'Screwfix: A Comprehensive Review of Screwfix.com.','screwfix, diy','Discount Codes for Screwfix - Screwfix Direct is UKs leading online and direct supplier of tools.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0');
